Inspire - teamwork skill
------------------------------------------------------------
A skilled swashbuckler in action is an imposing sight. A
swashbuckler experienced enough to use this ability knows
how to use his example of skill, and his sheer force of
presence to inspire others to fight better. Its effect is
similar to that of the Call to Arms, but non-Swashbucklers
can benefit from it as well.

GL: 14
SP: 60
command:  sinspire
duration: long
